headline: Agoda shares Asia's top three capital Cities that gave the best 'Bang for Your Buck' on New Year's Eve
summary: Cambodia's Phnom Penh emerged as the most affordable capital city to book New Year's Eve accommodations in Asia, according to digital travel platform Agoda. Booking insights analyzed by Agoda revealed that the average room in Phnom Penh costed no more than 67 USD on the final day of 2024.
